Text: This 'movie' was originally released under a different title, when I purchased it , it was titled as the filename indicates ... which begs the question ... do p()rn producers pirate from other p()rn producers?  Hmmm ;)

Once you get past that little detail and the blackout bars covering up something we're apparently not supposed to see, you get about 90 minutes of a fairly standard fuckfest starring some generally unattractive semi-natural and artificially-enhanced large-breasted females writhing for the camera. Oh, baby, oh, baby, oh, baby - mmm, yeah, mmm. Add a crappy sound-track and you pretty much have this summed up. If that's your cup of tea, knock yerself out.
